Speaker 2: Yeah, this is Tim Allen. I need to cancel my subscription.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: You know, you can order this as needed. You don't have to get it when you're not ready.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's what I said is that you can order it as needed.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Sounds great. Thank you.

Speaker 2: and you will have to call us to receive your next order.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: In that time frame, okay? And if you need more time, whatever the case is,

Speaker 1: we can leave it like this for the rest of your prescription, all right?

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: All right, if you want, I can give you my name and extension.

Speaker 2: I can put your orders in and make sure your account stays like this also, you know, if you choose to.

Speaker 1: What's your name?

Speaker 2: Quinn, Q-U-I-N-N.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: And my extension is 0035.

Speaker 1: 0035.

Speaker 2: Yes, sir, that is it.

Speaker 1: Okay, can you send me a confirmation or something, Quinn, saying that this has been taken off of automatic shipment?

Speaker 2: There's no confirmation.

Speaker 1: The reason I'm asking is because I didn't last time.

Speaker 2: I've already called once and requested this, and then I got another shipment.

Speaker 1: And so I need to make sure that it happens.

Speaker 2: You know what I mean?

Speaker 1: Oh, yeah, I know what happened.

Speaker 2: You got my extension, man.

Speaker 1: Trust me.

Speaker 2: You're not going to get anything else here.

Speaker 1: Like I said, for the next five months, everything is stopped.

Speaker 2: You're going to have to call us in that time to receive the next order.

Speaker 1: And basically how I do it is when you do call me in the next few months here,

Speaker 2: I'll push it out five months from the day you call,

Speaker 1: and we'll kind of just repeat that to let you keep doing it this way.

Speaker 2: Okay, that sounds great.

Speaker 1: Yeah, no worries.

Speaker 2: You got my extension and everything there, sir.

Speaker 1: I can reassure you that nothing will go out until you call me there, okay?

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Sounds good.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: You're welcome, sir.

Speaker 2: You have a great day.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye.
